resources.string: Phoenixsee is a man-made lake in Dortmund-Hoerde. It is located on the area of Phoenix-Ost, a former steel plant. People started to work on this lake in 2006 after a deal with Chinese investors who bought the steel plant and brought it to China. On October 1st 2010 the work on the lake were officially finished and since May 2011 everyone is allowed to go to the lake.
